1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,879
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,880 --> 00:00:31,959
=Episode 6=
(Love and hate entwine within me.)

3
00:00:31,960 --> 00:00:37,190
(You are no storied romance.
You are my inescapable tribulation.)

4
00:00:49,660 --> 00:00:51,460
(It's already been four hours.)

5
00:00:51,740 --> 00:00:53,660
(How much longer
does he need to stand here?)

6
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,900
Xihe was born heartless.

7
00:00:56,940 --> 00:00:59,180
Her body is covered in scars.

8
00:00:59,260 --> 00:01:01,860
Xihe was born heartless.

9
00:01:01,900 --> 00:01:03,900
Her body is covered in scars.

10
00:01:04,180 --> 00:01:05,340
Master.

11
00:01:06,180 --> 00:01:07,340
Master.

12
00:01:11,740 --> 00:01:14,100
Master.

13
00:01:17,060 --> 00:01:18,460
Master.

14
00:01:20,740 --> 00:01:21,779
Master.

15
00:01:21,780 --> 00:01:23,059
I found it.

16
00:01:23,060 --> 00:01:25,980
Xihe was born...

17
00:01:26,460 --> 00:01:27,820
Was born...

18
00:01:28,540 --> 00:01:30,020
Was born to bring misfortune.

19
00:01:31,380 --> 00:01:32,540
What?

20
00:01:35,260 --> 00:01:36,940
You keep staring at me.

21
00:01:37,020 --> 00:01:38,739
I'm so nervous that I forgot everything.

22
00:01:38,740 --> 00:01:40,660
Xihe was born heartless.

23
00:01:40,900 --> 00:01:42,500
Her body is covered in scars.

24
00:01:42,980 --> 00:01:44,420
She brings misfortune.

25
00:01:44,460 --> 00:01:45,979
If you wish to know about me,

26
00:01:45,980 --> 00:01:47,420
just ask.

27
00:01:48,060 --> 00:01:50,339
Why send such a charming lady

28
00:01:50,340 --> 00:01:51,740
on such an errand?

29
00:01:52,180 --> 00:01:53,459
It's no trouble.

30
00:01:53,460 --> 00:01:55,179
Master had me
get herbs to cure fever

31
00:01:55,180 --> 00:01:56,179
and ointment for frostbite.

32
00:01:56,180 --> 00:01:56,699
Baobao.

33
00:01:56,700 --> 00:01:57,860
Look.

34
00:01:58,820 --> 00:02:00,179
Use your divine sense.

35
00:02:00,180 --> 00:02:01,420
Why?

36
00:02:01,540 --> 00:02:02,979
There's no reason.

37
00:02:02,980 --> 00:02:04,140
Just use it.

38
00:02:05,060 --> 00:02:06,220
Oh.

39
00:02:06,260 --> 00:02:08,179
There's clothing
in the side hall's cabinet.

40
00:02:08,180 --> 00:02:09,420
Help her change into it.

41
00:02:09,460 --> 00:02:10,459
Remember.

42
00:02:10,460 --> 00:02:12,420
Don't say I had you take it.

43
00:02:14,900 --> 00:02:17,459
My lady, there's clothing
in the side hall.

44
00:02:17,460 --> 00:02:19,020
I'll help you change.

45
00:02:21,540 --> 00:02:24,619
He told you to help me?

46
00:02:24,620 --> 00:02:26,300
Master said not to say it.

47
00:02:33,340 --> 00:02:35,500
(Xihe was born heartless.)

48
00:02:35,900 --> 00:02:37,660
(Her body is covered in scars.)

49
00:02:38,100 --> 00:02:39,420
My lady,

50
00:02:39,740 --> 00:02:43,020
why are you covered in scars?

51
00:02:44,700 --> 00:02:46,420
You must be in pain.

52
00:02:50,220 --> 00:02:52,299
It's just some bruises.

53
00:02:52,300 --> 00:02:53,860
There are no scars.

54
00:02:55,820 --> 00:02:57,300
(In these hundred years,)

55
00:02:57,860 --> 00:03:00,140
(I've sketched her face countless times)

56
00:03:00,860 --> 00:03:03,740
(all for the day I can kill her
with my own hands.)

57
00:03:07,300 --> 00:03:09,580
Where did Baobao's intelligence
come from?

58
00:03:18,980 --> 00:03:20,860
Just a wildflower by the roadside.

59
00:03:21,700 --> 00:03:23,540
How dare you deceive me?

60
00:03:24,860 --> 00:03:26,659
I have already seen her once.

61
00:03:26,660 --> 00:03:28,460
She is a demigod now.

62
00:03:30,260 --> 00:03:33,020
Just come at me.

63
00:03:33,260 --> 00:03:34,740
Don't you dare harm her.

64
00:03:35,140 --> 00:03:36,740
In ancient times,

65
00:03:37,380 --> 00:03:39,580
the world could not tolerate a demigod.

66
00:03:40,100 --> 00:03:41,579
How dare a lowly god like you

67
00:03:41,580 --> 00:03:43,860
cause such great chaos?

68
00:03:44,820 --> 00:03:47,420
If the world's capacity is so narrow

69
00:03:47,700 --> 00:03:49,820
that it cannot accept a little girl,

70
00:03:50,300 --> 00:03:52,620
then let this world be cast aside.

71
00:03:52,820 --> 00:03:54,259
If you dare hurt her,

72
00:03:54,260 --> 00:03:56,300
I will risk everything in my cultivation

73
00:03:56,580 --> 00:03:59,819
to seek an explanation from the heavens.

74
00:03:59,820 --> 00:04:01,139
Do not forget your mission.

75
00:04:01,140 --> 00:04:03,300
You need not give me orders.

76
00:04:04,420 --> 00:04:06,180
I will never forget

77
00:04:06,660 --> 00:04:08,340
about finding the demon root.

78
00:04:08,820 --> 00:04:10,020
Answer me.

79
00:04:10,380 --> 00:04:12,140
I have returned from the dead.

80
00:04:12,300 --> 00:04:16,019
Is it because someone has
reshaped my flesh and blood?

81
00:04:16,020 --> 00:04:18,100
Heaven's secrets cannot be revealed.

82
00:04:19,980 --> 00:04:21,740
That sentence again.

83
00:04:24,860 --> 00:04:26,500
Does being the Heavenly Dao

84
00:04:27,020 --> 00:04:28,819
give you the right to toy
with the lives of all beings?

85
00:04:28,820 --> 00:04:29,499
Master.

86
00:04:29,500 --> 00:04:30,660
And if so, what of it?

87
00:04:31,100 --> 00:04:32,260
Master.

88
00:04:33,300 --> 00:04:34,620
Master.

89
00:04:42,300 --> 00:04:43,460
Master,

90
00:04:43,540 --> 00:04:45,139
I didn't close the main hall doors.

91
00:04:45,140 --> 00:04:46,659
That's why this beast slipped in,

92
00:04:46,660 --> 00:04:48,420
disrupting your cultivation.

93
00:04:49,140 --> 00:04:50,860
Have you encountered

94
00:04:51,580 --> 00:04:53,740
any strange occurrences in recent days?

95
00:04:54,100 --> 00:04:55,260
For instance,

96
00:04:56,460 --> 00:04:58,140
A talking duck?

97
00:04:58,700 --> 00:04:59,900
A duck?

98
00:05:02,820 --> 00:05:03,899
Well, not a duck.

99
00:05:03,900 --> 00:05:06,099
But there was a peddler who forcefully
tried to sell me an umbrella.

100
00:05:06,100 --> 00:05:06,979
He was a sleazy sort,

101
00:05:06,980 --> 00:05:08,139
tugging and pulling at me.

102
00:05:08,140 --> 00:05:09,460
It was truly annoying.

103
00:05:13,660 --> 00:05:14,779
If you encounter him again,

104
00:05:14,780 --> 00:05:16,019
do not pay any attention.

105
00:05:16,020 --> 00:05:16,899
Leave immediately.

106
00:05:16,900 --> 00:05:18,899
Okay. I shall punish this duck.

107
00:05:18,900 --> 00:05:20,580
I won't disturb
your cultivation any longer.

108
00:05:26,100 --> 00:05:27,019
My lady.

109
00:05:27,020 --> 00:05:29,339
is this the crispy, tender,

110
00:05:29,340 --> 00:05:32,219
oil-sizzling Beggar's Chicken?

111
00:05:32,220 --> 00:05:33,419
Indeed.

112
00:05:33,420 --> 00:05:34,580
Try it.

113
00:05:41,220 --> 00:05:43,780
Perhaps we should leave it
for Master.

114
00:05:53,340 --> 00:05:55,780
(Could my rebirth be because of you?)

115
00:05:56,140 --> 00:05:57,660
(Heavenly Dao, if you don't speak,)

116
00:05:57,900 --> 00:05:59,540
(I shall see for myself.)

117
00:06:03,460 --> 00:06:05,099
My lady, do not approach.

118
00:06:05,100 --> 00:06:06,659
Master is initiating
an Optical Rewind.

119
00:06:06,660 --> 00:06:08,300
You must not go near.

120
00:06:08,700 --> 00:06:09,980
What is an Optical Rewind?

121
00:06:10,020 --> 00:06:11,899
It is the ability to look back
upon past events.

122
00:06:11,900 --> 00:06:13,219
The cost is immense.

123
00:06:13,220 --> 00:06:14,019
A small mistake,

124
00:06:14,020 --> 00:06:15,580
and his soul will be destroyed.

125
00:06:15,780 --> 00:06:16,980
We shall leave.

126
00:07:00,980 --> 00:07:03,020
I was able to be reborn

127
00:07:04,260 --> 00:07:06,540
because Xi gave me her blood and flesh,

128
00:07:07,340 --> 00:07:09,460
piece by piece,

129
00:07:09,900 --> 00:07:11,660
to rebuild my soul.

130
00:07:25,580 --> 00:07:26,740
Baobao,

131
00:07:27,220 --> 00:07:29,899
did you use too much soap?

132
00:07:29,900 --> 00:07:30,899
There are so many bubbles.

133
00:07:30,900 --> 00:07:31,819
There are so many clothes.

134
00:07:31,820 --> 00:07:33,339
Of course, I added a bit more.

135
00:07:33,340 --> 00:07:34,860
Unlike me, who only has one set.

136
00:07:37,660 --> 00:07:38,459
Oh no.

137
00:07:38,460 --> 00:07:39,419
The full moon.

138
00:07:39,420 --> 00:07:40,579
I must block the moonlight.

139
00:07:40,580 --> 00:07:41,860
Or Master will be in danger.

140
00:07:54,140 --> 00:07:55,300
Baobao.

141
00:07:57,260 --> 00:07:58,420
Baobao?

142
00:07:58,460 --> 00:07:59,620
Xi.

143
00:08:14,490 --> 00:08:19,260
♪When starlight cuts
through the long night♪

144
00:08:21,700 --> 00:08:27,240
♪It bids farewell to another blue sky♪

145
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:29,889
♪To meet is to overlap♪

146
00:08:29,890 --> 00:08:31,799
♪To see is to part again♪

147
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:35,100
♪To stay is to wish for forever♪

148
00:08:36,540 --> 00:08:37,980
It must have hurt.

149
00:08:38,220 --> 00:08:40,220
What did you just call me?

150
00:08:41,140 --> 00:08:42,340
Xi?

151
00:08:43,140 --> 00:08:44,300
Xi.

152
00:08:51,540 --> 00:08:52,700
Master,

153
00:08:52,780 --> 00:08:54,980
I can't hold on any longer.

154
00:09:11,900 --> 00:09:13,740
You are really strange.

155
00:09:13,900 --> 00:09:15,860
You hugged me and called me Xi.

156
00:09:15,940 --> 00:09:17,820
Now, you push me away.

157
00:09:17,860 --> 00:09:19,220
It's truly baffling.

158
00:09:24,060 --> 00:09:25,419
Are you alright?

159
00:09:25,420 --> 00:09:26,580
Stay away!

160
00:09:27,940 --> 00:09:29,740
While I can still control myself,

161
00:09:29,860 --> 00:09:31,020
leave now.

162
00:09:32,860 --> 00:09:34,580
Can't you understand me?

163
00:09:34,900 --> 00:09:36,460
I told you to leave!

164
00:09:37,780 --> 00:09:38,939
There are Flower Slaves outside.

165
00:09:38,940 --> 00:09:40,220
I have nowhere to go.

166
00:10:04,780 --> 00:10:05,940
Ye Zhao?

167
00:10:14,860 --> 00:10:16,779
(No wonder he called me his wife.)

168
00:10:16,780 --> 00:10:18,139
(The woman in the painting)

169
00:10:18,140 --> 00:10:19,940
(truly looks just like me.)

170
00:10:32,900 --> 00:10:34,060
Ye Zhao?

171
00:10:34,900 --> 00:10:36,060
Is that you?

172
00:10:37,140 --> 00:10:38,300
Ye Zhao?

173
00:11:09,680 --> 00:11:11,359
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

174
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:14,239
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

175
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:16,959
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

176
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,599
♪Let the long shadows♪

177
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:24,200
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

178
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:25,839
♪If in a dream♪

179
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:28,599
♪I can hear your voice♪

180
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:31,439
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

181
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:34,039
♪Let it be us♪

182
00:11:34,040 --> 00:11:38,839
♪drawing endlessly close♪

183
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:40,599
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

184
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:43,240
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

185
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:46,199
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

186
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:47,839
♪Not even in time♪

187
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:53,519
♪to tell you how I feel♪

188
00:11:53,520 --> 00:11:55,039
♪If the rain won't stop♪

189
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:57,799
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

190
00:11:57,800 --> 00:12:00,759
♪Let love go on♪

191
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:03,319
♪Until forever♪

192
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:07,959
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

193
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:10,559
♪Until forever♪

194
00:12:10,560 --> 00:12:17,680
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
